  %% Diagram 80: Buyer Acquisition and Retention Loop Flow

  Discover[Discovery\nreels, live commerce, flash sales, SEO]
  FirstBuy[First purchase]
  Fulfill[Reliable fulfillment + trust signals]
  Engage[Post-purchase engagement\nnotifications, recommendations, wishlist alerts]
  Repeat[Repeat purchase]
  Loyalty[Loyalty effects\npoints, trust, habit formation]
  Refer[Referral and social sharing]

  Churn{Churn risk detected?}
  Winback[Win-back campaign\npersonalized offer or reminder]

  Discover --> FirstBuy --> Fulfill --> Engage --> Repeat --> Loyalty --> Refer --> Discover

  Engage --> Churn
  Repeat --> Churn
  Loyalty --> Churn
  Churn -- Yes --> Winback --> Engage
  Churn -- No --> Repeat
